# CODEOWNERS — midnightntwrk/servicedesk
#
# Default owners: @hegaleon and the @midnightntwrk/mn-sre team. The team
# co-ownership eliminates the previous single-point-of-failure on a single
# user for routine repo changes.
#
# Governance, security-policy and secret-touching files require
# @midnightntwrk/mn-security sign-off in addition to @hegaleon. mn-sre is
# intentionally NOT on these lines — separation of duties: SRE handles
# routine repo work, security handles policy and credentials.
# File set is standardized on the pattern used in other midnightntwrk
# repos (see midnightntwrk/midnight-node) and extended with the three
# workflows in this repo that hold live secrets / App credentials.

*                                           @hegaleon @midnightntwrk/mn-sre

# ── Governance + policy ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md                         @hegaleon @midnightntwrk/mn-security
/CODEOWNERS                                 @hegaleon @midnightntwrk/mn-security
/CONTRIBUTING.md                            @hegaleon @midnightntwrk/mn-security
/LICENSE                                    @hegaleon @midnightntwrk/mn-security

/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/config.yml    @hegaleon @midnightntwrk/mn-security

# Live on-call paging — uses PAGERDUTY_ROUTING_KEY secret
/.github/workflows/p1-pagerduty.yml         @hegaleon @midnightntwrk/mn-security
# ── GitHub config + scanning ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
/.github/dependabot.yml                     @hegaleon @midnightntwrk/mn-security
/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/                    @hegaleon @midnightntwrk/mn-security
/.github/PULL_REQUEST_TEMPLATE/             @hegaleon @midnightntwrk/mn-security
/.github/workflows/scan.yaml                @hegaleon @midnightntwrk/mn-security

# ── Secret-touching workflows (servicedesk-specific) ─────────────────────────
# p1-pagerduty.yml      — uses PAGERDUTY_ROUTING_KEY
# route-iac.yml         — uses IAC_APP_ID / IAC_APP_PRIVATE_KEY (GitHub App)
# route-shielded.yml    — reuses IAC_APP_ID / IAC_APP_PRIVATE_KEY for cross-org issue mirroring
/.github/workflows/route-iac.yml            @hegaleon @midnightntwrk/mn-security

# Published security policy — authoritative channel order and contact details
/SECURITY.md                                @hegaleon @midnightntwrk/mn-security

/.github/workflows/route-shielded.yml       @hegaleon @midnightntwrk/mn-security
